source.name: Paratransit Services - Vehicles
source.description: Paratransit Bases provide pre-arranged transportation for passengers with disabilities. Most of the services take individuals to and from health care facilities. This list includes detailed vehicle information, including affiliated base, license numbers, names(s) of licensees, DMV license plate and VIN numbers, license types, expiration date, and model year.
